				<td colspan="2"><span>Totally depends on the group situation.
<br />

<br />
I usually go for nivs(BoH),psalm,rondo,celerity,warsong (skip celerity if I am solo with Werewolf and mob is hitting me) plus SS bracer 9DS sometimes I will amp if I can for extra DS (no epic yet)
<br />

<br />
I do lots of fear kiting solo though with jonthans,warcry, largo, fear
<br />

<br />
My tactics are weird sometimes as I two box a 60cleric, so sometimes I just throw on assonance and haste and take the beating. The dual box with aoe mana works wonders for aaxp, and keeps the cleric FM.
<br />

<br />
Songs I am sure will change and you won't need celerity once you Epic. Which seems like you shall have it soon!<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
My common spell list for all occasions listed from top down
<br />

<br />
Jonthans, warcry, song of travel, chorus of replen, assonance, screech, absonant bindings, selo's
<br />

<br />
Later, Quip
<br />

<br />
I weild several combo's of Fleshgrinder, BoH, Darkmoon, and flameweaver as weapons.
<br />

<br />
Later.... again...<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
