				<td colspan="2"><span>I am a situational bard and my song line up constantly changes. One of the things I love is our versatility. We have so many tricks in our bag I do not think there is one right setup for anything. We can handle different situations in a multitude of ways.
<br />

<br />
So whats my suggestion? Find the song line up that best suits your play style and what you want to bring to the group. Once you do that you will be an uber Bard in your own right and your song line up and situational abilities will be all yours<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
