				<td colspan="2"><span>depends on the group
<br />

<br />
for *my* normal exp group.  I tend to do the 'ghetto ae' with myself and 2boxed cleric in group,  or with some melee friends (monk, his 2box cleric, bard guildmate,  rain, leesa in various combinations).  I usually play 55catana, 59dot (has a -mr debuff to it so play it before the next to help out a bit), 48 dot/slow.  Randomly hit things or pull when i need to with 60slow/dot.   So for this set up i have loaded da, selos, 55catana (these 3 have perma slots), 59aedot, 48aedot/slow, 60dot/slow,  51snare/slow, and then a random slot that i switch things around like tossing in dirge when im fm and goofing off.  
<br />

<br />
If im somewhere where the dots arent appropriate (the shrooms at zone in in the deep for example tend to resist too much for me) or with a fuller melee group,  i switch to (according to mood) rondos/psalms or rondos/warsong in for the 59/48 combo
<br />

<br />
